criteria.driver_alignment:
Reflect (explicit insights on value creation, risk drivers, and recommendation) — student states NPV interpretation, strategic considerations, and recommended action;  
Discover (context and objective) — clear statement of purpose and WACC;  
Validate/Evolve — benchmark validation and proposed enhancements support the reflective conclusions and next steps.

Discover: student states the analysis purpose and explicitly identifies 8.5% WACC as the discount rate;  
Implement: student applies the 8.5% WACC in the Python capital-budgeting model and computes NPV/IRR;  
Reflect: student validates the chosen WACC against a 8–10% industry benchmark and runs sensitivity tests with alternative WACCs.
